Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在堅定無比的內心裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}永遠以最堅強的節奏揭開案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}轉著轆轤的陶藝教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}對茶杯上的字興趣深深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}他的名字就是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.90,0:01:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}暗藏殺機的陶藝教室(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了小蘭 你看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}極真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}園子該不會連你也開始練習空手道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}你看清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}這上面明明寫的是 京極真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}你看成什麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我是開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}這個杯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}應該是你在現在去的那個陶藝教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}製作的茶杯對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}不過園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}你要把這個茶杯送給京極先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}難道不會嫌太小了一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實那個啊是我自己用的茶杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}這個才是送給阿真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}但是這上面怎麼寫的是你的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}這當然是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.90,0:02:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}要讓心愛的人在遙遠的異國星空下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}隨時隨地都能想起這裡還有我在關心他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}竟然只有寥寥幾通無聊又冷淡的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.40,0:02:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}我才會想到自己做一個特製的茶杯送給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼一來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}他就不會忘記我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}可是園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}你之前不是才送過他毛衣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}就是百貨公司買的那件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}後來我就沒送了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我想你說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}騙人總是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我就算拼命織件毛衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}他也只有冬天才能穿在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}可是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}送茶杯他就能每天用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我還是有點擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}阿真那個人對什麼人都好說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}要是被來路不明的女人纏著他就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.00,0:03:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好比說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}要是哪個自己老公先死了的寡婦聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他用那種溫柔的語調跟她說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}就一直纏著他之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他也真狠得下心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}為了替自己犯的錯贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}竟然讓這麼美的女人成了一個寡婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.40,0:03:51.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}如果不嫌棄我的胸膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}就儘管哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人 不能這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}可是偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}我 我真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:18.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}你怎麼了 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}對了園子 你以前跟我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你都是在每個星期日去上陶藝教室的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}對啊 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}你對這個也有興趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}是有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你做陶藝倒是挺有天分的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}美濃老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}不過這麼好的一個茶杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}寫上這些字實在太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}那到底是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}其實這也沒有什麼多大的意思啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}那你就好好的做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}快告訴我 你寫了什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這是秘密 我才不說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你該不會寫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}新一Love 之類的字眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那你就快點給我看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}讓我看一下又不會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k40}小弟弟有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你是跟學生一起來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}你們有誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}認識這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎麼來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}你該不會是跟在我們後面來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實是叔叔拜託我到這裡來看看情況的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}爸爸上個星期才來這裡參觀過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實這次是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}是新一對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我想這個小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}一定是受了新一的委託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}才到這來調查你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}這樣就知道你有沒有搞外遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}搞外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}新一哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}他怎麼有可能會做這麼蠢的事情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看你的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}就知道你拿了他的零用錢對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}你拿了多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}100
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}200
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}這麼少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}難得來了這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你想不想做些什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}應該沒關係吧 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}那麼就由我來親自做個樣本給你看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來你還曾經見過陶藝大師菊右衛門先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以那個大師的幾個徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}那時候就教了我幾個做陶藝的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}對不對 小蘭姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}怪不得你們兩個學起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}比一般人要快多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}這還真是不簡單呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}沒想到你們竟然認識那位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}國寶級的陶藝大師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}也沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}只是爸爸順便帶我去拜訪過而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}他們那裡正巧碰上了謀殺案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}小蘭的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}還順利的在短時間之內就破案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}你 你說破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}難不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}難道我爸爸上個星期來的時候沒有說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}其實我爸爸的名字叫做毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}經營了一家偵探事務所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說我就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}就是沉睡的小五郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}老實說他是我的偶像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}今天這挺熱鬧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}素夫 你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}其實我也是剛剛才到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}那麼岳父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我去換件衣服就來幫你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好意思阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說壽險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}投保這麼大的金額好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}是爸爸老說為了預防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}整天逼著我快點去幫他投保的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}以前說他是陶藝界最有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}成為陶藝大師的一把交椅我還相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}沒想到他女兒死了之後啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}人就完全變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}現在根本就是個喜歡玩泥巴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}沒用的醉老頭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你這麼說太刻薄了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}畢竟他可是你心愛亡妻的老爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}我心愛她個頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}我本來是想把那個老頭做陶藝賺來的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}看看能撈多少就撈多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}才對她提出離婚的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}沒想到那麼早就翹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}你也不用著急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}反正我看老師也活不了多少日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}等那老頭死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我們就把陶藝教室給收起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}出去另外開一家店怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}到時候只要把倉庫裡的作品賣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}應該也是一筆為數可觀的數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}那份保險的受益人登記的是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.30,0:08:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}當然是你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}畢竟我的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}從以前到現在就一直只有你的一個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我好高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}你願意為了我欠的那些錢去死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我不能呼吸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}岳父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我說菊代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我現在要去窯房那看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}那些學生就麻煩你照顧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}這條是新的領帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}那條領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}是菊代昨天晚上送給我的生日禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我還跟她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}其實呢我不太適合打米黃色的領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}其實這條領帶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}再適合你的脖子不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你就讓我看了一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k10}不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}反正杯子進窯的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k10}我說不行就不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你的杯子還不是會被大家看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.80,0:09:29.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}園子 你不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起 摔破了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我的杯子沒有摔破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那剛才那個聲音是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}好像是從倉庫傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}那我過去看一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}你要是偷看我們就絕交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}美濃老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我剛才滑了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}所以把盤子摔在地上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}能不能麻煩你幫我清理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.60,0:10:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}老師您怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.70,0:10:35.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}好像是這陶土裡面摻了什麼東西的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想也許是剛才打破的那個盤子的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}沾到我的衣服上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}那麼我去把急救箱拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你知道放在哪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}就在倉庫櫃子裡的右上方對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}那就麻煩你立刻幫我拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}您以後可要小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}對陶藝家來說手指就像生命一樣重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我的臉上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}不  沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}怎麼這麼久還沒有看到素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}剛才開始就沒看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}素夫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}窯房那裡也沒有看到他耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}現在就只剩下這個倉庫沒找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他不可能在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這個倉庫唯一能夠躲人的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}也只有這排櫃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}我剛才到這裡來拿急救箱的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}就已經開過櫃子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}裡面根本就沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個櫃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}那個櫃子的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}怎麼有塊布啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是陶藝教室裡穿的圍裙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}花色跟我們穿的圍裙一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}這人只記得藏頭就忘了藏尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.10,0:11:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}躲貓貓該玩夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}慢著 還是我來開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:19.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}素夫 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}素夫 素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}你快醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k30}素夫 素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}快點去叫救護車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.20,0:12:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}最好也把員警找來會比較妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}素夫 素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這次遭人勒死的人名叫美濃素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}今年31歲 是名上班族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}這名死者也是這間陶藝教室裡面的學生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}這裡是他住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}因為我那個兩年前去世的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就是他老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}至於我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}一直是這間陶藝教室的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}我叫美濃宗之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:12.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}旁邊這位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}則是我的助手笠間菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那麼請問被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}在回家之後都做了些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他下午五點左右回家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}本來他今天也像平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}回家就說要換上圍裙之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}就到陶藝教室這來幫我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我看他去了好一會都沒有看見他的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}才會跟大家分散開來一起找他的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}對吧 菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對 我們到處找過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最後就只剩下這個倉庫還沒找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}等到老師把櫃子打開來一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}素夫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}素夫他 素夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:50.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只不過你們也還真會找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}又不是在玩躲貓貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}你們怎麼知道櫃子裡會有人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}當然知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}因為圍裙跑出來了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}對吧 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}因為他穿的圍裙的一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當時剛好就從櫃子門邊的右下方露出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}你們知道那個衣角什麼時候露出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這 我就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}現在想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我們到這裡來清理盤子碎片的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}還沒有看到那條圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}什麼盤子的碎片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我今天不小心在櫃子前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}掉了一個盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}幾個學生聽到聲音趕到這來的時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我就請他們清理了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}我記得那個盤子正好是在素夫穿上圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}離開了這個倉庫之後才摔破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說你曾經跟被害人一起待在這個裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}因為陶藝教室的圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}平常都放在這個櫃子裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}所以素夫平常都是在這換上圍裙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}他的西裝外套也掛在這呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他的西裝外套旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}還掛了好幾件的薄布外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}這是做什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}那些外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}都是給學生上課的時候穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因為要製作大型水缸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}光穿圍裙根本就沒有辦法擋住衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那你當時和被害人在倉庫裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我本來在找菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}當時剛好看到菊代小姐和素夫在倉庫裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}當時我正在這裡幫素夫先生換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}後來老師也到了倉庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}說他要去窯房那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}叫我照顧一下學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}然後你怎麼回應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我就照老師說的立刻回教室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼 美濃先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}這個倉庫裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}就只剩你跟被害人兩個人了對不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}你先等一下 員警先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}你該不會懷疑是我殺了素夫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我剛才也說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}素夫換好衣服離開這裡的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}正好是在我把盤子弄掉之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}如果那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我就把他殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}塞進這個櫃子裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那麼在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}到這來幫我清理碎片的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}就應該會發現他的圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}在櫃子下面露出的那塊布頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}但是 也很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是在這些幫你清理的學生離開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}你為了確實被害人真的斷了氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}才不小心讓他的圍裙露出一角的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想應該沒有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}因為老師在我們還在清理碎片的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就到窯房那裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}等我們清理完畢回到教室的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}老師也已經回到教室裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}老師就一直在柯南的旁邊進行塑陶的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}老師從那個時候起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}到我們發現素夫先生的屍體之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}都一直跟我們這些學生在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}根本沒有時間將遺體塞進櫃子裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這麼說兇手應該是在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}小蘭你們把盤子的碎片清理完了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才把被害人找來了倉庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}加以殺害的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}再不就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}他先在什麼地方將被害人殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}再趁別人不注意的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}偷偷將屍體塞進了櫃子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我想菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}說不定曾經看到這名殺人兇手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}老實說我在塑陶的時候不小心割到了手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個時候呢我就請菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}到倉庫這來幫我拿急救箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當時正好是我們開始找素夫之前不久的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}所以我想她也許有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請問你 有看到誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}沒有 沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}那個急救箱平常都放在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}急救箱就放在右上方的櫃子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.50,0:17:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那你來的時候還開了門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}可是裡面沒人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}這是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}從死者頸部的痕跡看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}兇手行兇所使用的兇器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}應該就是纏在被害人脖子上的這條領帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是我就想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}兇手為什麼要將領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}纏在死者的脖子上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}可惜那條領帶是菊代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}送給素夫的生日禮物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}現在竟成了兇器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}那條領帶不是我送給他的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}可是他明明跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}這是你送給他的禮物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}其實 他曾經跟我提過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}他的皮箱裡不知道什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}放了一條附了張生日卡的領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}他還認定了那是我送的領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}只是不好意思承認而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}我突然想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}素夫走出倉庫的時候嘴裡還嘟嘟噥噥的說著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼金錢會讓一個人的心變成魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}雖然我昨天才過了31歲的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是我很有可能馬上就被魔鬼給吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他就會被鬼吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}其實不瞞你說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}關於這件事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 高木老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你去證實一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}小姐 請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你們這裡有沒有原子筆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}我的剛好沒水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那我去幫他拿好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我想教室裡應該會有原子筆才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是剪刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那個鑑識叔叔要老師找的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}應該是原子筆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}還有你快來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我做的茶杯馬上就要完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這麼看來你很喜歡陶藝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我好喜歡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我最討厭的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}想那個死掉的叔叔半途而廢的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}所以我一定會做完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}半途而廢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k30}你沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那個叔叔兩邊捲起來的袖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}長度根本就不一樣不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那樣看上去簡直就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.80,0:19:49.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}他是正在穿圍裙做準備工作的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.30,0:19:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才被兇手出其不意襲擊的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}他也有可能是跟兇手在糾纏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}無意中拉到了一邊的袖子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}對哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}那麼那個兇手一定也拉了他的領帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}因為他的領帶夾別的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}實在是太低了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}連那個洞口也被拉得好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過真是這樣的話也太低了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}他本來就喜歡把夾子別的那麼低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且呢說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}把兩邊的袖子捲成不同的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}也是他個人的喜好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}不過老師就喜歡把左右捲成一樣高吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}在那個叔叔從櫃子裡面倒下來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我記得老師本來是站在他左手邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}後來卻刻意的跨到他的右邊叫他不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}你那時候就是想他左右兩邊的袖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}捲成一樣的高度對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}而且我們本來只看到圍裙的衣角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}從櫃子的右端露了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}你只要開櫃子右邊的門就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}可是你卻把左右兩邊都打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.00,0:21:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k40}看到左右不對稱心裡就不踏實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}這是我做的茶杯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是不是做得很棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}做得還真是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}不過小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我看你心裡似乎有什麼疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你不是隱藏了什麼很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}就是正在做一個非常重大的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我猜對了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}因為陶土可是不會說謊的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}老師 你好厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你在對別人的問題追根究底之前呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}還是應該先把自己的問題解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}比較好一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這個可是老師你做的茶杯耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.60,0:21:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}我剛才趁著老師在抽屜裡面找東西的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就把老師的茶杯拿過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我本來以為老師應該會看得出來才對
